{"tid":1104340,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"麥包訓練班時期被指靚仔過城城","createTime":"2019-04-13T05:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T05:50:33.000Z","uid":71579,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b149afd257e71cc8b9169854ef0c8f69af74e65","tid":1104340,"uid":71579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:32:38.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】「仁濟醫院」昨晚在灣仔舉行第52屆董事局就職聯歡晚宴，多位圈中人也有出席，當中包括麥長青(麥包)、莊思敏、張秀文和快將結婚的嚴紀雯總理。剛有報道指，當年麥包在藝員訓練班時期，同班同學郭富城曾被導師指他樣貌不及麥包和林文龍兩位同學靚仔。<br />\n<br />\n以仁濟慈善大使身分到場的麥包笑着回答:「現在有版你睇，現在當然是他靚仔。哈哈！其實我不知當年導師曾有此說法，你問我的話，是沒有醜仔，每個同學都是靚仔，林文龍、城城還有邵仲衡都是同期學生，公司選得也是好的，那個年代劉德華、梁朝偉是偶像靚仔，總之那個似偶像，五官端正有打扮，青靚白正都是靚仔。」<br />\n<br />\n若然他現在減肥的話，會否真的會比城城更靚仔？麥包笑稱，不覺得自己會比城城靚仔，大家魅力不同，他說:「好我試試減磅，減磅到180磅。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，將於6月14及15連續兩日舉行婚禮的嚴紀雯被問到，正懷孕中的何超盈屆時是否會當姊妹團之一？嚴紀雯說:「她曾說過會來當姊妹，若然身體情況七話她會來，(超盈是否正身處美國待產？)不方便透露，但她應承了當姊妹，她應該會來的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FSsE8V8TWJ6VvvgO4v.xiQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTUxMg--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/FdWKl1Hw1C1KubQXVwkQ2w--~B/aD00MDA7dz01MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190413f085327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFSsE8V8TWJ6VvvgO4v.xiQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTUxMg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFdWKl1Hw1C1KubQXVwkQ2w--~B%2FaD00MDA7dz01MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190413f085327.jpg&h=e11485ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/celebrity/%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%8F%AD%E6%99%82%E6%9C%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9D%9A%E4%BB%94%E9%81%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%9F%8E-%E9%BA%A5%E5%8C%85-%E6%AF%8F%E5%80%8B%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E9%9D%9A%E4%BB%94-005000933.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fcelebrity%2F%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E7%258F%25AD%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259C%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%259D%259A%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%259F%258E-%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E5%258C%2585-%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%2583%25BD%25E4%25BF%2582%25E9%259D%259A%25E4%25BB%2594-005000933.html&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=3d5860c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/celebrity/%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%8F%AD%E6%99%82%E6%9C%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9D%9A%E4%BB%94%E9%81%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%9F%8E-%E9%BA%A5%E5%8C%85-%E6%AF%8F%E5%80%8B%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E9%9D%9A%E4%BB%94-005000933.html</a>"},{"pid":"6c98442fb145c3b348df470514ba8ddc9ae36968","tid":1104340,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"而家都係啦屌"},{"pid":"b35d0035b71d7f786936aedeff622ce2336d3f6f","tid":1104340,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:50:33.000Z","msg":"咁醜都靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}